name: Personalised and made to order - pull out cards
description:
Pull out cards with a personal touch. 
Suitable for any occasion - wedding, birth, birthday, anniversary etc....
This card will be made to your personal instruction:
The pictures is an example and will give you ideas that can be included in your card.
For a birth information needed would be name, time, date, weight 
Anniversary (1st, silver etc....) names or initials and date.
Birthday name, age.
Whatever you want please email to arrange jenlegg@tiscali.co.uk

name: Handbag Amy-evening bag with wired detail
description:
Handbag with the design feature of the handle enabling you to keep your bag close whilst carrying a round of drinks from the bar!
I will make to order so you can choose the colour way.
The bag has a magnetic closure.
Approx size is 24 by 24.
They are fully lined. 
They have a wired detail on the front 
Please contact me prior to order to discuss specifications jenlegg@tiscali.co.uk payment needs to be made before I make. Making up time up to 7 working days.
